Goodness gracious, what a treat. Imagine, if you will, hand crafted beers, perfectly made risotto, Cocktails that please the taste buds and make your head swim in swirls of pleasure. Imagine, a succulent lamb burger, with dinosaur kale and braised brussel sprouts, or fire roasted pizza pulled from a wood firing behemoth of a stove. Imagine, genuine, warm innovative owners, who welcome you, and clearly want you to enjoy. Now , Imagine all that at 2nd and christian in what once was The Lyon's Den the former dive bar. IMAGINE NO LONGER. KENNETT HAS ARRIVED AND SHE IS SPECTACULAR!
